                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280703-37-victim357 t18280703-37-viclabel196"></join> to a silversmith - we lodge in <placeName id="t18280703-37-crimeloc197">Golden Lion-court, Aldersgate-street</placeName>
